headline: Healthcare sector under pressure as market weighs Trump impact
summary: The S&P Biotech sector (XBI) has outperformed the S&P 500 (^GSPC) since 2021. Yahoo Finance Senior Health Reporter Anjalee Khemlani sits down with Catalysts host Madison Mills to take a closer look at the healthcare sector (XLV), specifically Medpace Holdings (MEDP) and Intuitive Surgical (ISRG), as uncertainty grows on the impact of President Trump's policy changes. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Catalysts here.
